WEBVTT FILE

1
00:04.600 --> 00:05.400
Hello everyone.

2
00:05.400 --> 00:08.766
I wanted to talk to you about something
that is close to my heart.

3
00:09.133 --> 00:11.800
Cyber security.

4
00:11.800 --> 00:14.500
Or actually what is even closer to my heart, which is digital.

5
00:14.633 --> 00:17.500
As you probably know, the thing with these two

6
00:17.500 --> 00:20.500
is that you can't have one without the other.

7
00:21.066 --> 00:24.866
As we take huge digital leaps across our company,

8
00:25.233 --> 00:29.766
cyber security becomes more than just a technical topic.

9
00:30.133 --> 00:32.666
It's a strategic foundation.

10
00:32.666 --> 00:37.866
It's what protects our company,
our employees, our customers, our end users,

11
00:37.900 --> 00:40.900
our factories and our suppliers.

12
00:41.866 --> 00:46.566
Cyber security is not just what we need to safeguard.

13
00:47.466 --> 00:50.800
Our customers, such as Heathrow Airport in London,

14
00:51.133 --> 00:54.100
set high expectations for us

15
00:54.100 --> 00:58.433
when it comes to securing our digital products
at their premises.

16
00:59.000 --> 01:03.600
We want to be worthy of their trust
and the trust of all our customers.

17
01:04.800 --> 01:06.100
This is possible by

18
01:06.100 --> 01:09.233
delivering on our promise securely every day.

19
01:10.333 --> 01:11.766
But here is the thing.

20
01:11.766 --> 01:15.633
Cyber security is not just for the experts, it's for all of us.

21
01:15.666 --> 01:19.766
Whether you are in R&amp;D operation, purchasing, or sales

22
01:19.766 --> 01:22.766
or in the field, your actions matter.

23
01:22.800 --> 01:26.800
We are all responsible for cyber security at today.

24
01:28.000 --> 01:31.000
Thanks for championing a cyber secure business.

25
01:31.200 --> 01:33.633
Let's rise together. Security.